  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/d127b165f9358853c5a5ecbcd2c73e49.poster.avif?t=1773048181\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/d127b165f9358853c5a5ecbcd2c73e49.webm?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/d127b165f9358853c5a5ecbcd2c73e49.mp4?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >● Master your Assault Suit!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the 2120s, as humanity expands into the cosmos, the \"Assault Suit\" stands as the ultimate humanoid weapon of war.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in high-stakes combat where heavy-metal giants dash across the stars, execute boost jumps, and unleash precision fire controlled by the advanced AIM system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As an Assault Suit pilot, the fate of the battlefield rests on your shoulders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/dacdec11bf5b593c0604439ccd20c109.poster.avif?t=1773048181\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/dacdec11bf5b593c0604439ccd20c109.webm?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/dacdec11bf5b593c0604439ccd20c109.mp4?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >● Customize and Conquer the Frontline!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic depth is the key to survival. Choose your machine and tailor your loadout by balancing range, firepower, ammo capacity, and elemental attributes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If your gear isn't up to the task, retreat and re-arm. If your performance isn't perfect, strike again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forge the ultimate, invincible machine optimized for any combat scenario.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/bd6d9c976d68aba21fac2a1861beec16.poster.avif?t=1773048181\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/bd6d9c976d68aba21fac2a1861beec16.webm?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/bd6d9c976d68aba21fac2a1861beec16.mp4?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >● Dynamic Battlefield Drama!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The tide of war shifts in real-time. Your allies are more than just NPCs—they react to your every move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you struggle against the enemy's onslaught, your squad suffers the consequences. If you clear objectives with lightning speed, you'll earn their respect and praise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The tension of the narrative and the rewards you reap depend entirely on your skill in the cockpit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/54d811e81e0cdef1d1ffb0c46f53e990.poster.avif?t=1773048181\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/54d811e81e0cdef1d1ffb0c46f53e990.webm?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/54d811e81e0cdef1d1ffb0c46f53e990.mp4?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >● Survive the Hardcore Combat with New Features!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate the most brutal missions using a suite of modern quality-of-life features.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize the Rewind function to undo mistakes, Quick Save & Load for tactical flexibility, and Mission Tips to find your edge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock support functions to boost your suit's durability and aim for 100% completion by mastering every machine and weapon through multiple playthroughs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/7ee90d4b5de0b78fb1ba7f6e72ecacbe.poster.avif?t=1773048181\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/7ee90d4b5de0b78fb1ba7f6e72ecacbe.webm?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/7ee90d4b5de0b78fb1ba7f6e72ecacbe.mp4?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >● About Assault Suit Leynos 2</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Originally released by MASAYA in 1997, this masterpiece defined the golden age of robot action games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the successor to the legendary Assault Suit Leynos (known as Target Earth in the West), it captivated players with its deep customization, heavy-metal handling, and a gripping battlefield drama that responds to the player's performance.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/d127b165f9358853c5a5ecbcd2c73e49.poster.avif?t=1773048181\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/d127b165f9358853c5a5ecbcd2c73e49.webm?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/d127b165f9358853c5a5ecbcd2c73e49.mp4?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >● Master your Assault Suit!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the 2120s, as humanity expands into the cosmos, the \"Assault Suit\" stands as the ultimate humanoid weapon of war.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in high-stakes combat where heavy-metal giants dash across the stars, execute boost jumps, and unleash precision fire controlled by the advanced AIM system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As an Assault Suit pilot, the fate of the battlefield rests on your shoulders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/dacdec11bf5b593c0604439ccd20c109.poster.avif?t=1773048181\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/dacdec11bf5b593c0604439ccd20c109.webm?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/dacdec11bf5b593c0604439ccd20c109.mp4?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >● Customize and Conquer the Frontline!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic depth is the key to survival. Choose your machine and tailor your loadout by balancing range, firepower, ammo capacity, and elemental attributes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If your gear isn't up to the task, retreat and re-arm. If your performance isn't perfect, strike again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forge the ultimate, invincible machine optimized for any combat scenario.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/bd6d9c976d68aba21fac2a1861beec16.poster.avif?t=1773048181\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/bd6d9c976d68aba21fac2a1861beec16.webm?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/bd6d9c976d68aba21fac2a1861beec16.mp4?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >● Dynamic Battlefield Drama!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The tide of war shifts in real-time. Your allies are more than just NPCs—they react to your every move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you struggle against the enemy's onslaught, your squad suffers the consequences. If you clear objectives with lightning speed, you'll earn their respect and praise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The tension of the narrative and the rewards you reap depend entirely on your skill in the cockpit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/54d811e81e0cdef1d1ffb0c46f53e990.poster.avif?t=1773048181\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/54d811e81e0cdef1d1ffb0c46f53e990.webm?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/54d811e81e0cdef1d1ffb0c46f53e990.mp4?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >● Survive the Hardcore Combat with New Features!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate the most brutal missions using a suite of modern quality-of-life features.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize the Rewind function to undo mistakes, Quick Save & Load for tactical flexibility, and Mission Tips to find your edge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock support functions to boost your suit's durability and aim for 100% completion by mastering every machine and weapon through multiple playthroughs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/7ee90d4b5de0b78fb1ba7f6e72ecacbe.poster.avif?t=1773048181\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/7ee90d4b5de0b78fb1ba7f6e72ecacbe.webm?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488300/extras/7ee90d4b5de0b78fb1ba7f6e72ecacbe.mp4?t=1773048181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >● About Assault Suit Leynos 2</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Originally released by MASAYA in 1997, this masterpiece defined the golden age of robot action games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the successor to the legendary Assault Suit Leynos (known as Target Earth in the West), it captivated players with its deep customization, heavy-metal handling, and a gripping battlefield drama that responds to the player's performance.</p>",
